result:
<v-form v-model="valid">
    <v-text-field
        v-model="nomeCompleto"
        :rules="nomeCompletoRules"
        label="Nome Completo"
        required
    ></v-text-field>
    <v-text-field
        v-model="matricula"
        :rules="matriculaRules"
        mask="#########"
        label="Num de Matrícula"
        required
    ></v-text-field>
    <v-text-field
        v-model="curso"
        :rules="cursoRules"
        label="Curso do Aluno"
        required
    ></v-text-field>
    <v-select
        v-model="categoria"
        :items="categorias"
        label="Categoria"
    ></v-select>
    <v-btn color="success" @click="salvarAluno">Salvar </v-btn>
    <v-btn color="error"  @click="fechaDialogo">Voltar </v-btn>
</v-form>
